title: 637. Takeaways from CFP National Championship Game + Reaction to Doug Pederson Firing
itunes:title: 637. Takeaways from CFP National Championship Game + Reaction to Doug Pederson Firing
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a special new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys give their takeaways from the College Football Playoff National Championship game between Alabama and Ohio State, while focusing on the top prospects (:56). Then, the pair focus on Alabama wide receiver DeVonta Smith and debate if he should go in the top 5 of the 2021 NFL Draft (18:18). To wrap up the show, the duo react to the Philadelphia Eagles firing head coach Doug Pederson and discuss if he would be a good candidate for the New York Jets' head coaching vacancy (28:16). Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
